/20190109103327qp5r2OCIbe3yFPui.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>设计师：Natalie Rushton</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109103329RyW386rY1XxBMqfH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>设计师：Liu Chen</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109103334K79tTBVnWzLjHq4u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>设计师：Liu Chen</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109103337hMS4LCe3fPp2J9Fr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>设计师：Daoyuan Ding</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901091033399rHVO6UTMjeXwW21.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>设计师：Daoyuan Ding</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://fashionfav.com/magazine-editorials/hen-yanni-x-imre-van-opstal-sarah-blais/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>L’officiel Italia </em>2018 年 12 月造型特辑：Hen &amp; Imre。</a></strong><br></p><p>模特：Hen Yanni X Imre Van Opstal，摄影：Sarah Blais，造型：Monika Tatalovic。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109101552VXauJkwhlzmSFvdQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.320000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109101552eU9WZ8HFfRMAV5ka.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.310000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109101549kr9640fU8mzj1PET.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.237500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901091015506hRQbem49gSYPI8n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.323750\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109101551cDCFbJN2ozVBsYwq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.325000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109101550RcIe6bOrPi3lfhqH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.339000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109101549Radvjm8isQkBeq4O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.227500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109101551vxgP2HheUsDwZ3pG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.325000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109101549gYufahCoxc0IUdNs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.812500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109101647zY21NwSb3ACQtxT9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://metalmagazine.eu/en/post/editorial/blood-brothers-suraj-nongmaithem\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>Metal Magazine</em>&nbsp;男装造型特辑：Blood Brothers。</a></strong><br></p><p>摄影：Suraj Nongmaithem，造型：Kayleigh Swan。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109102219IO6wML7PmbC5ZFHQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109102220V37KfJjblpTwG2Lg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.508011\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109102220r1XAGYOfMtac4zSV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109102220TtrCgn03LG96Slux.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109102312SnXr6TlUvp03xwEc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109102231QXZ8GRavErx4ou9i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109102231vj4NrTVK06flswRd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109102231LyBCiRcJPjgsehGq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109102335EtCJfRLeBFD0wd3g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109102232c1SEt8lG2fDpUHhW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>自 2015 年起，Foam（荷兰阿姆斯特丹摄影博物馆）每年都会组织一个名为 Foam Talent Call 的年轻摄影师评选活动，在全球选出 20 名年龄在 18 - 35 岁的摄影师，将他们的作品集中展示，并进行全球巡展。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/art-photography/article/42780/1/foam-talent-2019-maisie-cousins-durimel-amsterdam-london-new-york-frankfurt\" rel=\"nofollow\">Foam Talent 2019 选出的 20 名摄影师包括来自中国的何博和陈哲等。</a></strong>他们的作品将于 1 月 13 日至 3 月 3 日在阿姆斯特丹展出，接下来会先后在纽约（3 月 22 至 4 月 8 日）、伦敦（5 月 16 至 6 月 10 日）以及法兰克福（5 月 24 至 8 月 26 日）巡展。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901091059193AIGLYTcySg9MuWf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414677\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>“Ants” from the series grass, peonies, bum, 2018 © Maisie Cousins / Courtesy of the artist and TJ Boulting</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109105919Zy6usTUab2edroYO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.199219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>“A Nice Day with some fruit” from the series Flowers for Donald, 2017 © Gregory Eddi</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109105943NjTgF38tkGLWslAQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Tank Reel from the series The Studio Sculptures © Jaya Pelupessy</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901091059434O0zowmjGpx3NEcs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>From the series Studies in Geology, 2017 © Stelios Kallinikou, courtesy of the artist</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109105956GJS6tuk1y9gEYbX4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.260835\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>“Kaelyn and the girls” from the series Frères dune île pas très proche, 2018 © Durimel</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109105918li3Rq1MDzPK98QIS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.526718\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Model Angela and her personal story”, 2016, from the series Separation Anxiety, 2018- ongoing © Dima Komarov</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109110005ZRBSI60TY9WMXvEm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>RMX2040” from the series Your next step would be to do the Transmission © Valentine Bo</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901091100208Phc6BzfX7gpi0QC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>“Untitled” from the series How to Secure a Country, 2015-2018 © Salvatore Vitale</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109110042wyx9AHd54JtCsOWR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>“Untitled” from the series Worry for the Fruit the Birds Won’t Eat, 2018 © Sophie Gabrielle</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109110102NflPsZ4j8TMqGCX7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>From the series Separation Anxiety, 2018-ongoing © Dima Komarov</figcaption> </figure></div><p>题图来自摄影师 Dima Komarov 系列项目“Seperation Anxiety”</p>"}